				<wikidot:authorName>DrChandra</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1956625</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This is just a silly little sequel to the previous tale, since I can't very well give Lolly a hovercraft and not show her using it.</p> <p>I'm aware there's not a lot of real tension in this tale, since there's never any real doubt they're going to survive, but it really is just supposed to be a short, silly space adventure. At least one beta reader took an issue with all the science terms I used here, but you can't get to space without science.</p> <p>Thanks to everyone in chat who gave me feedback on this.</p> 
				 	]]>
